      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "One for the babies. BOOMELLI (1) resumes here but the form she showed in her first campaign was good enough for a race of this calibre. Revved up for this with a recent trial win and shapes as a key runner while fresh. Goes on top and thinking she wins this before measuring up in better company. READY AS BAM (2) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and Richardson sticks in the saddle for race day. Gets some favours from the inside alley and shapes up as the main danger ahead of LONESOME STAR (6) who has gotten better with each run and gets in well at the weights with the claim. In the mix. KISKABOOM (5) next best by default.",
